asmai vârksha*m* da*nd*a*m*. 25. su*s*ravas su*s*ravasa*m* meti. 26.
samidham âdadhyâd Agnaye samidham iti. 27. bhaiksha*m* *k*aren. 28.
mâtaram agre. 29. <sup>ऽ</sup>thânyâs suh*ri*da. 30. â*k*âryâya
bhaikshan nivedayet. 31. tish*th*ed âstamayât tûsh*n*î*m*. 32.
trirâtra*m* kshâralava*n*e dugdham iti var*g*ayet.

